eval forms can be found to support all these theories, and it is possible that several names have fallen together, or that the name was subjected to reanalysis by folk etymology at an early date."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Geoffrey de Marisco had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Geoffrey de Marisco."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1130–1179":"1130–1179","1155–1213":"1155–1213","1170–1245":"1170–1245","–Female":"Surnud","1213":"1213","1245":"1245","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1130":"1130","about 1155":"umbes 1155","1170":"1170","Castle, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Iirimaa","Shanid, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Iirimaa"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1130–1179":"1130–1179","1155–1213":"1155–1213","1170–1245":"1170–1245","–Female":"Kuollut","1213":"1213","1245":"1245","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1130":"1130","about 1155":"noin 1155","1170":"1170","Castle, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irlanti","Shanid, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irlanti"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1130–1179":"1130–1179","1155–1213":"1155–1213","1170–1245":"1170–1245","–Female":"Décédée","1213":"1213","1245":"1245","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1130":"1130","about 1155":"environ 1155","1170":"1170","Castle, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irlande","Shanid, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irlande","lifeSummary":"Geoffrey de Marisco a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Geoffrey de Marisco."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1130–1179":"1130–1179","1155–1213":"1155–1213","1170–1245":"1170–1245","–Female":"Verstorben","1213":"1213","1245":"1245","1179":"1179","1155":"1155","1130":"1130","about 1155":"um 1155","1170":"1170","Castle, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irland","Shanid, Limerick, Ireland":"County Limerick, Irland","lifeSummary":"Geoffrey de Marisco hatte mit Geoffrey de Marisco mindestens 1 Sohn und 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","1130–1179":"1130–1179","1155–1213":"1155–1213","1170–1245":"1170–1245","–Female":"Desede","1213":"1213","1245":"1245","1179":"1179","1155":"1155